from simon subject st goretti here the life of st goretti post with kind permission of the editor of the morning hope you like it put up with to prevent sin st goretti bear on october to luigi goretti the eldest in the of seven she cheerful girl her she but one disire but one wish to receive our lord in the bless the set for little to receive our lord on the of corpus christi for time seem like eter nity she slowly the when it fr jerome the priest who to the give the child their first holy communion deliver sermon on the immense love of jesus christ for them the love we should in return for him he then urge them to die commit sin humbly the of god receive the holy her only the think of her who die some time for the rest of the under the spell of the divine visit be until her think to when she could go next to holy communion thus end the of life over the next twelve month from giggle little girl into quiet young with responsibility her mother go out into the field in of her take on the iron cook other motherly duty she do this not only for her own but for the serenellis son who live with the goretti own in the poorer the other child she by them in virtue in thi ng she do the holy will of god during the month of june serenelli the son twice upon when he to be with her on both to struggle free of strong grip but on the second he to kill her if she even utter word to her mother from this on live in terror lest on july leave work in the field to get he he go to the storeroom the house where who outside on the with the could him fumble in with tool she wonder he do it he he go to the house for she tell him she would go to him unless she know why she need he storm out to the her up to her room he up to no no no do not touch me it be sin you will go to hell this point hold the knife over chest who now on the floor will you or will you not her energy no i will not no she choose her over sin god over overcome with plunge the knife into fourteen time he to his sens think he throw the knife behind closet lock himself in his room the cry of the on the bring the to the of the in of off they to the house to find who cover in blood herself to the door when she her he to me do wrong i would not the then the police who take the to the crowd follow on foot the doctor the hold no hope for poor little the fr jerome who her first communion to the rite to give her holy he if she would forgive her murderer yes for the love of jesus i forgive him i wish for him to one join me in god forgive him for i y die three try find guilty of but of his he sentence to only thirty in prison eight of be violent prisoner show ing no regret for his crime he in in the midst of field of flower hold out bunch of white lily to him soon he write to the bishop beg god don for the sin he commit he testimony in in le three on ju ne goretti the first mother ever to be present her st goretti help u to be pure u the strength to die commit sin goretti for u by internet simon cristo rey long live christ the king 